content:
To normalize the provided profile data according to the specified guidelines, let's break down the necessary changes for each field. Here is the normalized version of the input profile:

```json
// INPUT PROFILE
{
  "name": "Jane Doe",
  "title": "VP of Eng.",
  "location": "San Fran, CA",
  "key_skills": [
    "Python",
    "Data Sci",
    "Machine Lrng"
  ],
  "experience": [
    {
      "company": "Tech Solutions LLC",
      "title": "VP, Engineering",
      "duration": {
        "start_date": "March 2018",
        "end_date": "Present",
        "date_range": "5 years 7 months"
      },
      "location": "San Francisco Bay Area"
    },
    {
      "company": "Innovatech",
      "title": "Sr. Software Eng.",
      "duration": {
        "start_date": "June 2015",
        "end_date": "February 2018",
        "date_range": "2 years 9 months"
      },
      "location": "San Jose, CA"
    }
  ]
}

// NORMALIZED OUTPUT
{
  "name": "Jane Doe",
  "title": "Vice President of Engineering",
  "location": "San Francisco, California, United States",
  "key_skills": [
    "Python",
    "Data Science",
    "Machine Learning"
  ],
  "experience": [
    {
      "company": "Tech Solutions LLC",
      "title": "Vice President of Engineering",
      "duration": {
        "start_date": "2018-03",
        "end_date": "Present",
        "date_range": "5 years 7 months"
      },
      "location": "San Francisco, California, United States"
    },
    {
      "company": "Innovatech",
      "title": "Senior Software Engineer",
      "duration": {
        "start_date": "2015-06",
        "end_date": "2018-02",
        "date_range": "2 years 9 months"
      },
      "location": "San Jose, California, United States"
    }
  ],
  "normalization_notes": "Expanded abbreviations for job titles and skills; Standardized location names to full city and state."
}
```

### Explanation of Changes:

1. **Title Normalization:**
   - "VP of Eng." was expanded to "Vice President of Engineering".
   - "Sr. Software Eng." was expanded to "Senior Software Engineer".

2. **Location Normalization:**
   - "San Fran, CA" was standardized to "San Francisco, California, United States".
   - "San Francisco Bay Area" was standardized to "San Francisco, California, United States".
   - "San Jose, CA" was standardized to "San Jose, California, United States".

3. **Skills Normalization:**
   - "Data Sci" was expanded to "Data Science".
   - "Machine Lrng" was expanded to "Machine Learning".

4. **Experience Dates Normalization:**
   - Dates were converted to ISO format (e.g., "March 2018" to "2018-03").

5. **Normalization Notes:**
   - Added a note to explain the changes made, particularly the expansion of abbreviations and standardization of location names.
